des: The Nail Tech Network is just that! A Network for students and teachers that would love to share their own styles and techniques to show others around the world what’s really going on in the world of Nail Technicians! Nails are really hot right now so we had to create a fun zone for this niche and we did just that. The information in this skill is provided for informational and educational purposes only.
